Package game.randomevent

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    RandomEvent
    Represents a random event such as the Team getting robbed or gifted an item.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    RandomEventType
    Denotes a kind of random event that can occur when the Team visits a City.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ItemGiftedException
    Represents the random event that a Team receives a gift per Section 2.3 of the specification
    ItemRobbedException
    Represents the random event that a Team gets an Item robbed per Section 2.3 of the specification
    MoneyRobbedException
    Represents the random event that a Team gets money robbed per Section 2.3 of the specification
    RobberyPreventedException
    Prevents a team from being robbed if there is a Law Student in the team
